\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">3</span> \n					</p>\n				</td>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0pt;color:#366092;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">配置前端控制器</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"> web.xml</span> \n					</p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						&nbsp;\n					</p>\n				</td>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">&lt;servlet&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;servlet-name&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">springmvc</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/servlet-name&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;servlet-class&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background:yellow;\">org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;/servlet-class&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#BFBFBF;\">&lt;!-- </span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#BFBFBF;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>DispatcherServlet</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">的初始化方法在执行时，会启动</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Spring</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">容器，</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#BFBFBF;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">所以，需要指定</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Spring</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">配置文件的位置</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#BFBFBF;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>--&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;init-param&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;param-name&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">contextConfigLocation</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/param-name&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;param-value&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">classpath:spring-mvc.xml</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/param-value&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;/init-param&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;load-on-startup&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">1</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/load-on-startup&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>&lt;/servlet&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>&lt;servlet-mapping&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;servlet-name&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">springmvc</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/servlet-name&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&lt;url-pattern&gt;</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">*.do</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;/url-pattern&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>&lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<div>\n	<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:845px;\" class=\"ke-zeroborder\" height=\"564\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0pt;color:#366092;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">4</span> \n					</p>\n				</td>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0pt;color:#366092;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">配置控制器与视图映射器</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"> spring-mvc.xml</span> \n					</p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						&nbsp;\n					</p>\n				</td>\n				<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#A6A6A6;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">&lt;!-- </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">配置</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">HandlerMapping\n  --&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;bean class=\"</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background:yellow;\">org.springframework.web.servlet.handler.SimpleUrlHandlerMapping</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">\"&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"margin-left:.375in;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;property\n  name=\"</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">mappings\"</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"margin-left:.75in;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;color:#FF0066;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">&lt;props&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"margin-left:1.125in;font-size:10.5pt;color:#A6A6A6;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:微软雅黑;\">&lt;!-- </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:微软雅黑;\">匹配请求路径，可以有非常非常多个，但名字要唯一，与下面的</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;\">Bean</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:微软雅黑;\">的</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;\">id</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:微软雅黑;\">要一致</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-family:微软雅黑;\"> --&gt;</span> \n					</p>\n					<p style=\"margin-left:1.125in;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">\n						<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#FF0066;\">&lt;prop key=\"</span><span style=\"fo